\lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\frac{\arccos(1 - x)}{\sqrt{x}} = \sqrt{2}\,\,\,\cdots (1)
f(x) = \frac{1}{x}\cdot\arccos\left(\left(\frac{1 - x^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\right)^{\cos x}\right)
\begin{aligned}L &= \lim_{x \to 0^{+}}f(x)\\ &= \lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\frac{1}{x}\cdot\arccos(1 - z)\\ &= \lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\frac{1}{x}\cdot\sqrt{z}\cdot\frac{\arccos(1 - z)}{\sqrt{z}}\\ &= \sqrt{2}\lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\sqrt{\dfrac{z}{x^{2}}}\text{  (using (1))}\\ &= \sqrt{2}\lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\sqrt{\dfrac{1 - y}{x^{2}}}\,\,\,\cdots (2)\end{aligned}
\begin{aligned}1 - y &= 1 - \left(\frac{1 - x^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\right)^{\cos x}\\ &= 1 - \left(1 - \frac{2x^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\right)^{\cos x}\\ &\geq 1 - \left(1 - \frac{2x^{2}\cos x}{1 + x^{2}}\right)\\ &= \frac{2x^{2}\cos x}{1 + x^{2}}\,\,\,\cdots (3)\end{aligned}
\begin{aligned}1 - y &= 1 - \left(\frac{1 - x^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\right)^{\cos x}\\ &= 1 - \left(1 - \frac{2x^{2}}{1 + x^{2}}\right)^{\cos x}\\ &\leq 1 - (1 - 2x^{2})^{\cos x}\\ &\leq 1 - (1 - 2x^{2})\\ &= 2x^{2}\,\,\,\cdots (4)\end{aligned}
\frac{2\cos x}{1 + x^{2}}\leq \frac{1 - y}{x^{2}} \leq 2
\lim_{x \to 0^{+}}\frac{1 - y}{x^{2}} = 2
